{"TopicId":191520,"ForumId":24,"TopicTitle":"Hello, and please excuse the future mess","CreatedByName":"GEPEG_Unconscious","CreatedById":202743,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-10T01:30:41Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"GEPEG_Unconscious","CreatedById":202743,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-10T01:30:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHI all,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have been an avid KSP player and forum viewer since the days of 1.0.5, but only recently felt the desire to post stuff. I figure this topic would be a good place to figure out the forum formatting, hence the potential for future messes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhawk","CreatedById":131400,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-10T02:04:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/202743-gepeg_unconscious/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022202743\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/202743-gepeg_unconscious/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@GEPEG_Unconscious\u003C/a\u003E and welcome to the KSP Forums!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t worry about the mess.\u00A0 The space janitor will clean it up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nHappy landings!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GEPEG_Unconscious","CreatedById":202743,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-10T02:13:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheers to that \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/131400-starhawk/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022131400\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/131400-starhawk/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Starhawk\u003C/a\u003E. Space janitors are important jobs after all.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes the @ callout notify the linked user every time a topic is updated, or only when a post mentions the callout specifically?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhawk","CreatedById":131400,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-10T02:50:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe @ notifies you only when it is posted.\u00A0 Threads you start are on your notify list by default, so you get notified every time somebody posts in one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nHappy landings!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GEPEG_Unconscious","CreatedById":202743,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-10T04:10:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s good to know, thank you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet\u0027s see what a picture looks like.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImgur\u0027s BBcode:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022gOfQyZd.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/gOfQyZd.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHTML:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0026lt;a href=\u0022https://imgur.com/gOfQyZd\u0022\u0026gt;\u0026lt;img src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/gOfQyZd.png\u0022 title=\u0022source: imgur.com\u0022 /\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNever done picture posting before, so I do not know which format is preferred here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GEPEG_Unconscious","CreatedById":202743,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-10T04:13:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, it seems HTML is very much not the way to go, so the other format it is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpoiling the fun:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022v8f9irl.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/v8f9irl.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022I9PfgKG.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/I9PfgKG.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-10T05:34:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve always used Imgur\u0027s BBCode version.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-10T05:49:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can also just paste an image link and the forum will magic it into the image.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, links to the forum are similarly treated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GEPEG_Unconscious","CreatedById":202743,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-11T03:09:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll good things to know. Thanks all!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne last thing to play with: quoting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EYou can also just paste an image link and the forum will magic it into the image.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223738682\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022191520\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221581313762\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can also just paste an image link and the forum will magic it into the image.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, links to the forum are similarly treated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerballingSmasher","CreatedById":195689,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-11T19:10:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, that\u0027s the forums in a nutshell.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Retro Starship","CreatedById":200667,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-14T19:05:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EWelcome to the KSP forum \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/202743-gepeg_unconscious/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022202743\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/202743-gepeg_unconscious/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@GEPEG_Unconscious\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0even though you have been playing way longer than me.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003ENew here\u00A0myself\u00A0since the end of last year, but yea so much fun with KSP and this forum.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}